msgstr "文章批量写入计划必须包含有界的草稿操作组。"

#: includes/Governance/Plan_Proposal_Service.php:410
msgid "Article batch write plans must include one reviewed article artifact set per draft action."
msgstr "文章批量写入计划必须为每个草稿操作包含一组已审核文章工件。"

