msgid "Article media batch write plans must contain a bounded group of draft, media upload, and featured-image actions."
msgstr "文章媒体批量写入计划必须包含有界的草稿、媒体上传和特色图片操作组。"

#: includes/Governance/Plan_Proposal_Service.php:544
msgid "Article media batch write actions must be objects."
msgstr "文章媒体批量写入操作必须是对象。"

#: includes/Governance/Plan_Proposal_Service.php:556
msgid "Article media batch plans may target only draft and allowlisted media actions."
msgstr "文章媒体批量计划只能面向草稿和允许列表中的媒体操作。"

#: includes/Governance/Plan_Proposal_Service.php:578
msgid "Article media batch plans must include create, upload, and featured-image actions for every article."
msgstr "文章媒体批量计划必须为每篇文章包含创建、上传和特色图片操作。"

