msgid "Image candidate adoption actions must be objects."
msgstr "图片候选采用操作必须是对象。"

#: includes/Governance/Plan_Proposal_Service.php:645
msgid "Image candidate adoption plans may target only media import, metadata, and featured-image abilities."
msgstr "图片候选采用计划只能面向媒体导入、元数据和特色图片能力。"

#: includes/Governance/Plan_Proposal_Service.php:664
msgid "Image candidate adoption plans must include exactly one media upload and one metadata action, plus at most one featured-image action."
msgstr "图片候选采用计划必须正好包含一个媒体上传和一个元数据操作，并最多包含一个特色图片操作。"

#: includes/Governance/Plan_Proposal_Service.php:684
msgid "Image candidate adoption action input must remain dry-run and must not request commit."
msgstr "图片候选采用操作输入必须保持试运行，且不得请求提交。"

